NUMBER 1512
NAME Thunderchild, Cargo Hold
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
EXIT S 1513
*DESCRIPTION_START
The spacious hold is stacked with orderly rows of crates and barrels
holding provisions for several weeks at the very least. Off to one side
are several stacks of wooden boxes marked with the names of various
members of the Order. To the south, a narrow corridor leads to the
crew's quarters, and a door is set into the northern wall. An opening
leads to stairs back up to the decks and a ladder protrude from an open
hatchway, leading down.
*DESCRIPTION_END
