NUMBER 1027
NAME Thunderchild, Lower Level
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
ITEM 0 335 VAL2=1512
ITEM 1 72 VAL2=1030
ITEM 2 72 VAL2=1033
*DESCRIPTION_START
A narrow dimly lit corridor runs the length of the ship. Here and there,
light shines from openings and doorways into the corridor, and the
sounds of building and settling in fill the air. At the far end of the
corridor is an opening that leads into a small forge.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
NUMBER 1030
NAME Forge
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
FORGE
CALL 33
;
;forge
ITEM 0 1517
;opening
ITEM 1 72 VAL2=1027
;bin
ITEM 2 1416
;bellows
ITEM 3 1518
;
*DESCRIPTION_START
Here in the lowest levels of the ship, a makeshift forge has been set
up. The wooden floor is carefully paved around the platform that holds a
small forge to protect it from cinders and embers that might fly while a
smith is working. An older drakin, his wings battlescarred, sits guard
over the small stockpile of steel, almost grudgingly doling it out on
request. A narrow opening leads back out into the corridor.
*DESCRIPTION_END

;
IFPREVERB PUSH 3
  CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You pump the bellows, sending a blast of air over the burning coals in the forge, causing them to glow with an intense, fiery red heat.
    ECHO OTHERS %N pumps the bellows, sending a blast of air over the burning coals in the forge, causing them to glow with an intense, fiery red heat.
ENDIF
