NUMBER 1033
NAME Chapel
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
EXIT O 1027
*DESCRIPTION_START
The walls of this small room are paneled with a light wood that seems to
hold and reflect the light, giving the air a soft shimmer. Against this
background are framed the lineages of various Drakin Clans. There is
little other ornamentation, but the clean, uncluttered room is pleasing
to the eye and mind. Benches and kneelers of pale oak are interspersed
with flat cushions and pads, offering a choice of many positions in
which to meditate. 
*DESCRIPTION_END

NUMBER 1513
NAME Thunderchild, Belowdecks
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
EXIT N 1512
*DESCRIPTION_START
A narrow, dimly lit corridor divides the ship in two. At regular
intervals along both sides of the hall are openings closed by sliding
screens that offer at least a modicum of privacy for the higher ranking
members of the crew. A narrow flight of stairs leads back up to the
deck, and the light brightens considerably to the north. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
